---

Controls the trigger mode of the device, and whether automatic functions are invoked. For example, this parameter can be used to automatically activate a scanning device when placed in a shopping cart, holster or other designated location. When trigger Mode is set to Off (option 0, **the default**), all scanning requires manual triggering by the device user. 
